{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Treasure Atlas, players move their characters around the map by interacting with various events located on the map. These events can include buffs, debuffs, monster encounters, and dungeons. In turn-based battles, players use their decks to defeat enemies and advance their exploration of the world.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">World generation: each playthrough takes place on a new map, providing unique challenges and opportunities to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deck building: as you progress through the game, assemble a unique deck, making each adventure unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn-based battles: Each turn requires strategic choices to defeat enemies and use your deck and resources effectively.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In an ancient and mysterious world of many continents, a harmonious kingdom once thrived, ruled by wise mages and valiant warriors. However, an ancient curse has torn this world into separate regions plunged into chaos. Now adventurers explore the remnants of a great civilisation, seeking to restore the lost greatness and unravel the secrets of the past.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unstoppable Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2757450/4c1f0d56b6377bde15e215c3623dda610850bfda.jpg"},{"name":"Halfway to Glory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2757450/4c1f0d56b6377bde15e215c3623dda610850bfda.jpg"},{"name":"First Island Treasures Collected \u2014 New Frontiers Ahead!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2757450/4c1f0d56b6377bde15e215c3623dda610850bfda.jpg"},{"name":"Gold Seeker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2757450/4c1f0d56b6377bde15e215c3623dda610850bfda.jpg"},{"name":"Trader","pat